milestones.description: Viswanath has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 254 runs, going past Brijesh Patel's 233
Wettimuny has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SL breaking Tissera's record
Wettimuny has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (32) in an innings in ODIs for SL, going past Wettimuny's 28
Wettimuny's 67 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing Tennekoon's 59
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for IND, going past Viswanath
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for SL, going past Tony Opatha
Wettimuny and Roy Dias's 96-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 82 between Tissera and Tennekoon
Wettimuny and Warnapura's 31-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Fernando and Wettimuny
Wettimuny and Roy Dias's 96-run partnership is SL's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 54 between Wettimuny and Warnapura
Pasqual and Duleep Mendis's 52-run partnership is SL's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Tissera and Duleep Mendis
Pasqual and de Silva's 11-run partnership is SL's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Mevan Pieris and Ranasinghe
